1. main obj
- Blog Application with simple CRUD Functionalities

2. Target User?
- user and admin

3. Core features
- sign up 
- login
- Create Blog (User) 
- Read all available post (User(can view specific post))
- Update post (User/ Own post(optional))
- Delete post (User/ Own post(optional))
- Add Comment (User/ Own post(optional))
- Delete any post (Admin)
    

4. Data
- User (firstname, lastname, email, password, isAdmin)
- Post (headline, introduction, mainContent, date, author, comments(subdoc array))

5. Tech Requirement
- Express.js API, MongoDB with Mongoose for data storage and management, RESTful Architecture.

6. Security
- token, bcrypt hash

7. Routes and cont
Controller:
- register
- login
- addPost (All User)
- getAllPost (All User)
- viewPostDetail (All User)
- deletePost (Admin and User(optional))

optional:
- updatePost
- getAllComment
- addPostComment

Routes:
- POST /register
- POST /login
- POST /addPost
- GET /getAllPost
- GET /viewPost/:postId
- DELETE /deletePost/:postId

optional
- PATCH /updatePost/:postId
- POST /:postId/comments
- GET /getAllComments